skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dad jokes
des:
Dad Jokes is a simple skill which tells you a lame joke.
Ask Alexa to open Dad Jokes and simply say something like "Tell me a dad joke" to use the skill.
Say "One more" or "Another one" to hear another
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
